title: Indian Restaurant
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Indian restaurant operated by a friendly couple who speak some English. Offers a vegetarian option for the set meal each day. Directions: Take tram 2 or 3 to 味噌天神前 Misotenjinmae, walk southeast 200 yards to a major junction including a petrol station, take a sharp left so you are now walking north, continue for 400 yards, and on your left will be the restaurant. Japanese address 熊本県熊本市大江5-12-11-1.
